Available Tools: set_temperature | get_temperature | set_mode | get_schedule
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "device_id": "string", "temperature": number, "mode": "heat|cool|auto|off" }
Response Schema: { "device_id": "string", "current_temp": number, "target_temp": number, "mode": "string" }

Question: Please set the patio thermostat to 21 degrees.
Call: { "func_call": "set_temperature", "device_id": "thermostat_patio_11", "temperature": 21, "mode": "auto" }
Response: { "device_id": "thermostat_patio_11", "current_temp": 19.8, "target_temp": 21, "mode": "auto" }

Question: What is the temperature reading in the library right now?
Call: { "func_call": "get_temperature", "device_id": "thermostat_library_12", "temperature": 0, "mode": "auto" }
Response: { "device_id": "thermostat_library_12", "current_temp": 20.4, "target_temp": 22, "mode": "heat" }

Question: It is too warm in the den; lower it to 20 degrees.
Call: { "func_call": "set_temperature", "device_id": "thermostat_den_13", "temperature": 20, "mode": "cool" }
Response: { "device_id": "thermostat_den_13", "current_temp": 23.1, "target_temp": 20, "mode": "cool" }

